lead_paragraph: Thomas Voeckler, the popular French veteran rider, secured overall victory in the Tour de Yorkshire on Sunday with a sprint finish triumph in the 198km final stage from Middlesbrough to Scarborough.

headline.print_headline: Voeckler Wins Tour of Yorkshire After Sprint Finish
